---

This project's cross-platform port-inspection approach was inspired by, and
adapted from, the following MIT-licensed projects. Thank you to their authors:

- portcop (https://github.com/Hawila/portcop) — MIT — the per-OS listening-port
  discovery + kill strategy (lsof / ss / netstat + tasklist).
- portrm  (https://github.com/abhishekayu/portrm) — MIT — the idea of service
  identification and safety tiers per listening port.
